# ==========================================
# MODEL CHECKPOINTS (Exclude, but keep main models)
# ==========================================
# Keep: face_v2_enhanced (1)/ with config.json & model.safetensors
# Keep: omni_detector_v1/ with config.json & model.safetensors
# Exclude: checkpoint-* directories (they're large and redundant)
*/checkpoint-*/
!face_v2_enhanced\ \(1\)/
!face_v2_enhanced\ \(1\)/config.json
!face_v2_enhanced\ \(1\)/model.safetensors
!face_v2_enhanced\ \(1\)/preprocessor_config.json
!omni_detector_v1/
!omni_detector_v1/config.json
!omni_detector_v1/model.safetensors
!omni_detector_v1/preprocessor_config.json

# ==========================================
# IMPORTANT: KEEP THESE MODELS
# ==========================================
# The model directories are required for the system to work
# They contain trained weights for:
# - face_v2_enhanced (1): Fine-tuned face deepfake detector
# - omni_detector_v1: Whole-image authenticity detector
# - aispy_efficientnet: EfficientNet model data

